Key Features and Benefits of the Automatic Light System
Smart Motion-Based Lighting: The IR sensor detects movement and triggers the LED to blink three times before staying ON.
Hands-Free Operation: Automatically controls lighting without the need for manual switches.
Security Enhancement: Acts as a deterrent by turning on the light when motion is detected.
Energy Efficiency: Reduces unnecessary power consumption by ensuring lights activate only when needed.
Continuous Illumination: The LED remains ON even when no motion is detected, ensuring visibility.
Ideal for Various Locations: Suitable for staircases, hallways, garages, and entryways.
Easy Integration: Can be incorporated into home automation and security systems.
Low Maintenance: Requires minimal user intervention for operation.
